{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kamu-penakut-atau-bukan-yuk-buktikan-dengan-baca-komik-ini/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kamu Penakut atau Bukan? Yuk, Buktikan dengan Baca Komik ini!","content":"<p>Nggak bisa dipungkiri kalau saat ini banyak orang yang mengemari apapun yang berbau horor, seperti acara tv, film, dan juga komik. Semakin seram ceritanya, semakin dapat membuat orang penasaran. Tapi, kadar takut seseorang akan hal berbau horor pastinya berbeda-beda. Ada yang penakut, ada juga yang berani.</p>\n<p>Selain itu, banyak orang yang berfikir kalau hal-hal yang berbau horor ini cuma cerita belaka alias nggak nyata. Namun gimana ya kalau kejadian-kejadian horor yang biasa kamu tonton atau baca tenyata ada di sekitarmu? Ihh, pasti seram dan bikin bulu kuduk merinding!</p>\n<p>Buat kamu penggemar komik horor online, coba deh baca komik <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/hitam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hitam</a>. Sesuai judulnya, kamu akan di bawa ke dalam kegelapan yang menakutkan pada hal-hal yang sebelumnya mungkin nggak pernah terpikirkan. Eits, bacanya jangan malam-malam dan sendirian ya! Bisa-bisa kamu nggak bisa tidur karena ketakutan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45421\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45421\" data-attachment-id=\"45421\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kamu-penakut-atau-bukan-yuk-buktikan-dengan-baca-komik-ini/attachment/hitam4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45421\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45421\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Pernah pulang larut malam? Kalau pernah, apa sih yang terlintas dibenakmu kalau kamu menemukan anak kecil yang menangis sendirian di tengah jalanan sepi? Lari atau malah disamperin?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45422\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45422\" data-attachment-id=\"45422\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kamu-penakut-atau-bukan-yuk-buktikan-dengan-baca-komik-ini/attachment/hitam5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45422\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45422\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Kayaknya kamu harus pikir ulang deh kalau mau nyamperin. Siapa tau anaknya kayak gini. Duh, nggak kebayang deh kalau hal ini benar-benar terjadi. Bisa-bisa kamu langsung lari terbirit-birit.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45417\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45417\" data-attachment-id=\"45417\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kamu-penakut-atau-bukan-yuk-buktikan-dengan-baca-komik-ini/attachment/hita3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hita3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber : CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber : CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.gith