/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam7.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45424\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Hayo, di sini siapa yang kalau tidur harus selalu pakai guling? Emang sih guling itu bikin tidur makin nyenyak, berasa ada yang bisa dipeluk-peluk gitu deh. Tapi, pernah nggak sih kamu kepikiran kalau guling itu mirip sama pocong?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45423\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45423\" data-attachment-id=\"45423\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kamu-penakut-atau-bukan-yuk-buktikan-dengan-baca-komik-ini/attachment/hitam6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45423\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hitam6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45423\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Duh, kalau ternyata yang di peluk bukan guling dan malah pocong, gimana ya? Nyenyak atau malah makin mimpi buruk? Coba sebelum tidur, cek dulu gulingnya. Siapa tau udah berubah jadi yang lain. Hihi.</p>\n<p>Masih ada banyak cerita horor yang bisa kamu baca di komik<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/hitam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Hitam</a>. Tinggal buka aja aplikasi<em>Â </em><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics,</a> ya! Eits, kamu juga bisa loh nuangin kreatifitas cerita horor kamu ke dalam komik dengan ikutan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-challenge-vol-3-total-hadiahnya-450-juta-rupiah/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>CIAYO Comics Challenge Vol.3</strong></a>. Ada banyak hadiah yang bisa kamu dapatkan.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"3427e62a-f35d-504f-898e-4bfa51de31af"}}}